    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just a mild headache tho, not like a huge migraine or anything. i don't want to bother my doctor for something this small. if i just took a single low dose, like like 200mg, would that even be a big deal for my kidneys? it feels like it would be fine for just a one-time thing.",
